exceptions.exn: Unable to find an instance for the variables x, y.

In environment H : forall x y : bool, Is_true (eqb x y) -> x = y Unable to unify "{p : PrimRec ?M1504 | extEqual ?M1504 (evalPrimRec ?M1504 p) (charFunction ?M1504 (notRel ?M1504 ?M1505))}" with "{p : PrimRec 2 | extEqual 2 (evalPrimRec 2 p) (charFunction 2 (fix eqb (n m : nat) {struct n} : bool := match n with | 0 => match m with | 0 => true | S _ => false end | S n' => match m with | 0 => false | S m' => eqb n' m' end end))}".

original: unfold Nat.eqb. rewrite <- Bool.eqb_eq. apply notRelPR. pose (neqIsPR). apply (sig_rec _ _ _ neqIsPR). intro x. destruct x. apply H.
